import React from 'react';
import Calendario from '../../components/Calendario';
import * as C from './styles';
import { FontAwesomeIcon } from '@fortawesome/react-fontawesome';
import { faUser, faCalendarDays } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons';

const Home = () => {
    return (
        <C.Container>
            <C.Navbar>
                <C.NavbarContent>
                    <C.IconContentLogo>
                        <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faCalendarDays} />
                    </C.IconContentLogo>
                    <C.IconGroup>
                        <C.IconContent>
                            CL
                        </C.IconContent>
                        <C.IconContent>
                            CT
                        </C.IconContent>
                        <C.IconContent>
                            TM
                        </C.IconContent>
                    </C.IconGroup>
                    <C.IconContent>
                        <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faUser} />
                    </C.IconContent>
                </C.NavbarContent>
            </C.Navbar>
            <C.CalendarContainer>
                <C.CalendarContent>
                    <Calendario />
                </C.CalendarContent>
                <C.DateInfoContent>
                    Informações do calendario
                </C.DateInfoContent>
            </C.CalendarContainer>
        </C.Container>
    )
}

export default Home
